77. Classify the various network functions which provide network information or functions.
PHP has functions for network info:
•	gethostbyname() → Gets IP of hostname
•	gethostbyaddr() → Gets hostname by IP
•	gethostbynamel() → Returns list of IPs for hostname
•	getservbyport() → Service by port number
•	getprotobyname() / getprotobynumber() → Protocol details
•	ip2long() and long2ip() → Convert IP formats
